SYNOPSIS

    In your weaver.ini:

     [-Acme::CPANLists]

DESCRIPTION

    This plugin is used when building Acme::CPANLists::* distributions. It
    currently does the following:

      * Create "AUTHOR LISTS" POD section from @Author_Lists

      * Create "MODULE LISTS" POD section from @Module_Lists

      * Mention some modules in See Also section

      e.g. Acme::CPANLists (the convention/standard), acme-cpanlists (the
      CLI tool), etc.

SEE ALSO

    Acme::CPANLists

    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Acme::CPANLists

